  <h2>How this gravel calculator works</h2>
  <p>The calculator multiplies length &times; width &times; depth to estimate volume, converts cubic feet to cubic yards, and estimates weight using your selected gravel density.</p>
  <h2>Why gravel density matters</h2>
  <p>Pea gravel, river rock, crushed stone, and compacted base can weigh different amounts. Use your supplier's density for the most accurate estimate.</p>
